{"surah":82,"verses":[{"n":1,"key":"82:1","arabic":" إِذَا ٱلسَّمَآءُ ٱنفَطَرَتْ","page":587,"juz":30,"en":"When the sky breaks apart","id":"Apabila langit terbelah,","words":[{"a":"إِذَا","en":"When","id":"apabila"},{"a":"ٱلسَّمَآءُ","en":"the sky","id":"langit"},{"a":"ٱنفَطَرَتْ","en":"(is) cleft asunder","id":"terbelah"}]},{"n":2,"key":"82:2","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلْكَوَاكِبُ ٱنتَثَرَتْ","page":587,"juz":30,"en":"And when the stars fall, scattering,","id":"dan apabila bintang-bintang jatuh berserakan,","words":[{"a":"وَإِذَا","en":"And when","id":"dan apabila"},{"a":"ٱلْكَوَاكِبُ","en":"the stars","id":"bintang-bintang"},{"a":"ٱنتَثَرَتْ","en":"scatter","id":"jatuh bertaburan"}]},{"n":3,"key":"82:3","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلْبِحَارُ فُجِّرَتْ","page":587,"juz":30,"en":"And when the seas are erupted","id":"dan apabila lautan dijadikan meluap,","words":[{"a":"وَإِذَا","en":"And when","id":"dan apabila"},{"a":"ٱلْبِحَارُ","en":"the seas","id":"lautan"},{"a":"فُجِّرَتْ","en":"are made to gush forth","id":"dijadikan meluap"}]},{"n":4,"key":"82:4","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلْقُبُورُ بُعْثِرَتْ","page":587,"juz":30,"en":"And when the [contents of] graves are scattered [i.e., exposed],","id":"dan apabila kuburan-kuburan dibongkar,","words":[{"a":"وَإِذَا","en":"And when","id":"dan apabila"},{"a":"ٱلْقُبُورُ","en":"the graves","id":"kuburan-kuburan"},{"a":"بُعْثِرَتْ","en":"are overturned","id":"di bongkar"}]},{"n":5,"key":"82:5","arabic":"عَلِمَتْ نَفْسٌ مَّا قَدَّمَتْ وَأَخَّرَتْ","page":587,"juz":30,"en":"A soul will [then] know what it has put forth and kept back.","id":"(maka) setiap jiwa akan mengetahui apa yang telah dikerjakan dan yang dilalaikan(nya).","words":[{"a":"عَلِمَتْ","en":"Will know","id":"mengetahui"},{"a":"نَفْسٌۭ","en":"a soul","id":"jiwa"},{"a":"مَّا","en":"what","id":"apa"},{"a":"قَدَّمَتْ","en":"it has sent forth","id":"diusahakan"},{"a":"وَأَخَّرَتْ","en":"and left behind","id":"dan ditinggalkan"}]},{"n":6,"key":"82:6","arabic":"يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلْإِنسَـٰنُ مَا غَرَّكَ بِرَبِّكَ ٱلْكَرِيمِ","page":587,"juz":30,"en":"O mankind, what has deceived you concerning your Lord, the Generous,","id":"Wahai manusia! Apakah yang telah memperdayakan kamu (berbuat durhaka) terhadap Tuhanmu Yang Maha Pengasih.","words":[{"a":"يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا","en":"O","id":"wahai"},{"a":"ٱلْإِنسَـٰنُ","en":"man","id":"manusia"},{"a":"مَا","en":"What","id":"apa"},{"a":"غَرَّكَ","en":"has deceived you","id":"yang menipu kamu"},{"a":"بِرَبِّكَ","en":"concerning your Lord","id":"terhadap Tuhanmu"},{"a":"ٱلْكَرِيمِ","en":"the Most Noble","id":"Mulia/Pemurah"}]},{"n":7,"key":"82:7","arabic":"ٱلَّذِى خَلَقَكَ فَسَوَّىٰكَ فَعَدَلَكَ","page":587,"juz":30,"en":"Who created you, proportioned you, and balanced you?","id":"Yang telah menciptakanmu lalu menyempurnakan kejadianmu dan menjadikan (susunan tubuh)mu seimbang,","words":[{"a":"ٱلَّذِى","en":"Who","id":"yang"},{"a":"خَلَقَكَ","en":"created you","id":"telah menciptakan kamu"},{"a":"فَسَوَّىٰكَ","en":"then fashioned you","id":"lalu Dia menyempurnakan kamu"},{"a":"فَعَدَلَكَ","en":"then balanced you","id":"lalu Dia menjadikan kamu seimbang"}]},{"n":8,"key":"82:8","arabic":"فِىٓ أَىِّ صُورَةٍ مَّا شَآءَ رَكَّبَكَ","page":587,"juz":30,"en":"In whatever form He willed has He assembled you.","id":"dalam bentuk apa saja yang dikehendaki, Dia menyusun tubuhmu.","words":[{"a":"فِىٓ","en":"In","id":"dalam"},{"a":"أَىِّ","en":"whatever","id":"apa saja"},{"a":"صُورَةٍۢ","en":"form","id":"gambar/bentuk"},{"a":"مَّا","en":"what","id":"apa"},{"a":"شَآءَ","en":"He willed","id":"yang Dia kehendaki"},{"a":"رَكَّبَكَ","en":"He assembled you","id":"Dia menyusunmu"}]},{"n":9,"key":"82:9","arabic":"كَلَّا بَلْ تُكَذِّبُونَ بِٱلدِّينِ","page":587,"juz":30,"en":"No! But you deny the Recompense.","id":"Sekali-kali jangan begitu! Bahkan kamu mendustakan hari pembalasan.","words":[{"a":"كَلَّا","en":"Nay","id":"sekali-kali jangan"},{"a":"بَلْ","en":"But","id":"tetap/bahkan"},{"a":"تُكَذِّبُونَ","en":"you deny","id":"kamu mendustakan"},{"a":"بِٱلدِّينِ","en":"the Judgment","id":"pada hari pembalasan"}]},{"n":10,"key":"82:10","arabic":"وَإِنَّ عَلَيْكُمْ لَحَـٰفِظِينَ","page":587,"juz":30,"en":"And indeed, [appointed] over you are keepers,","id":"Dan sesungguhnya bagi kamu ada (malaikat-malaikat) yang mengawasi (pekerjaanmu),","words":[{"a":"وَإِنَّ","en":"And indeed","id":"dan sesungguhnya"},{"a":"عَلَيْكُمْ","en":"over you","id":"atas kalian"},{"a":"لَحَـٰفِظِينَ","en":"(are) surely guardians","id":"sungguh ada penjaga"}]},{"n":11,"key":"82:11","arabic":"كِرَامًا كَـٰتِبِينَ","page":587,"juz":30,"en":"Noble and recording;","id":"yang mulia (di sisi Allah) dan yang mencatat (perbuatanmu),","words":[{"a":"كِرَامًۭا","en":"Noble","id":"yang mulia"},{"a":"كَـٰتِبِينَ","en":"recording","id":"yang mencatat"}]},{"n":12,"key":"82:12","arabic":"يَعْلَمُونَ مَا تَفْعَلُونَ","page":587,"juz":30,"en":"They know whatever you do.","id":"mereka mengetahui apa yang kamu kerjakan.","words":[{"a":"يَعْلَمُونَ","en":"They know","id":"mereka mengetahui"},{"a":"مَا","en":"whatever","id":"apa"},{"a":"تَفْعَلُونَ","en":"you do","id":"kamu kerjakan"}]},{"n":13,"key":"82:13","arabic":"إِنَّ ٱلْأَبْرَارَ لَفِى نَعِيمٍ","page":587,"juz":30,"en":"Indeed, the righteous will be in pleasure,","id":"Sesungguhnya orang-orang yang berbakti benar-benar berada dalam (surga yang penuh) kenikmatan,","words":[{"a":"إِنَّ","en":"Indeed","id":"sesungguhnya"},{"a":"ٱلْأَبْرَارَ","en":"the righteous","id":"orang-orang yang baik"},{"a":"لَفِى","en":"(will be) surely in","id":"benar-benar dalam"},{"a":"نَعِيمٍۢ","en":"bliss","id":"kesenangan/kenikmatan"}]},{"n":14,"key":"82:14","arabic":"وَإِنَّ ٱلْفُجَّارَ لَفِى جَحِيمٍ","page":587,"juz":30,"en":"And indeed, the wicked will be in Hellfire.","id":"dan sesungguhnya orang-orang yang durhaka benar-benar berada dalam neraka.","words":[{"a":"وَإِنَّ","en":"And indeed","id":"dan sesungguhnya"},{"a":"ٱلْفُجَّارَ","en":"the wicked","id":"orang-orang durhaka"},{"a":"لَفِى","en":"(will be) surely in","id":"dalam"},{"a":"جَحِيمٍۢ","en":"Hellfire","id":"neraka"}]},{"n":15,"key":"82:15","arabic":"يَصْلَوْنَهَا يَوْمَ ٱلدِّينِ","page":587,"juz":30,"en":"They will [enter to] burn therein on the Day of Recompense,","id":"Mereka masuk ke dalamnya pada hari pembalasan.","words":[{"a":"يَصْلَوْنَهَا","en":"They will burn (in) it","id":"mereka masuk kedalamnya"},{"a":"يَوْمَ","en":"(on the) Day","id":"hari"},{"a":"ٱلدِّينِ","en":"(of) the Judgment","id":"pembalasan"}]},{"n":16,"key":"82:16","arabic":"وَمَا هُمْ عَنْهَا بِغَآئِبِينَ","page":587,"juz":30,"en":"And never therefrom will they be absent.","id":"Dan mereka tidak mungkin keluar dari neraka itu.","words":[{"a":"وَمَا","en":"And not","id":"dan tidaklah"},{"a":"هُمْ","en":"they","id":"mereka"},{"a":"عَنْهَا","en":"from it","id":"dari padanya"},{"a":"بِغَآئِبِينَ","en":"(will be) absent","id":"dengan gaib/meloloskan diri"}]},{"n":17,"key":"82:17","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدْرَىٰكَ مَا يَوْمُ ٱلدِّينِ","page":587,"juz":30,"en":"And what can make you know what is the Day of Recompense?","id":"Dan tahukah kamu apakah hari pembalasan itu?","words":[{"a":"وَمَآ","en":"And what","id":"dan apakah"},{"a":"أَدْرَىٰكَ","en":"can make you know","id":"kamu melihat"},{"a":"مَا","en":"what","id":"apa"},{"a":"يَوْمُ","en":"(is the) Day","id":"hari"},{"a":"ٱلدِّينِ","en":"(of) the Judgment","id":"pembalasan"}]},{"n":18,"key":"82:18","arabic":"ثُمَّ مَآ أَدْرَىٰكَ مَا يَوْمُ ٱلدِّينِ","page":587,"juz":30,"en":"Then, what can make you know what is the Day of Recompense?","id":"Sekali lagi, tahukah kamu apakah hari pembalasan itu?","words":[{"a":"ثُمَّ","en":"Then","id":"kemudian"},{"a":"مَآ","en":"what","id":"apakah"},{"a":"أَدْرَىٰكَ","en":"can make you know","id":"kamu melihat"},{"a":"مَا","en":"what","id":"apa"},{"a":"يَوْمُ","en":"(is the) Day","id":"hari"},{"a":"ٱلدِّينِ","en":"(of) the Judgment","id":"pembalasan"}]},{"n":19,"key":"82:19","arabic":"يَوْمَ لَا تَمْلِكُ نَفْسٌ لِّنَفْسٍ شَيْـًٔا ۖ وَٱلْأَمْرُ يَوْمَئِذٍ لِّلَّهِ","page":587,"juz":30,"en":"It is the Day when a soul will not possess for another soul [power to do] a thing; and the command, that Day, is [entirely] with Allāh.","id":"(Yaitu) pada hari (ketika) seseorang sama sekali tidak berdaya (menolong) orang lain. Dan segala urusan pada hari itu dalam kekuasaan Allah.","words":[{"a":"يَوْمَ","en":"(The) Day","id":"hari"},{"a":"لَا","en":"not","id":"tidak"},{"a":"تَمْلِكُ","en":"will have power","id":"berdaya/berkuasa"},{"a":"نَفْسٌۭ","en":"a soul","id":"manusia"},{"a":"لِّنَفْسٍۢ","en":"for a soul","id":"bagi diri/seseorang"},{"a":"شَيْـًۭٔا ۖ","en":"anything","id":"sesuatu/sedikitpun"},{"a":"وَٱلْأَمْرُ","en":"and the Command","id":"dan urusan"},{"a":"يَوْمَئِذٍۢ","en":"that Day","id":"pada hari itu"},{"a":"لِّلَّهِ","en":"(will be) with Allah","id":"bagi Allah"}]}]}